posting_body: ['$420 PLUS TAX / 1br - 450ft2 - Extended stay (San Dimas, CA)', 'THE RATE IS FOR ONE WEEK 7 DAYS.', 'Please Call On The Day You Need The Room After 3PM', 'As We Do Not Make Reservations', 'And All Rooms Are 1st', 'Come First Serve.', 'Choose from one king bed or two queen beds depending on which is available.', 'Each room includes a microwave and large refrigerator, housekeeping service once per week, we offer guest laundry, pool and spa.', 'SOME rooms have cooktops with kitchen cabinets.', 'We also provide free Wi-Fi.', 'Limit of 2 persons per room with 1 bed and limit 4 persons per room with 2 beds.', 'A $100 CASH deposit is required at the time of check in and is refundable upon checkout pending room check.', 'RATE DOES NOT INCLUDE TAX.']
